{"type": "article", "id": 8541, "title": "儿童帐篷", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-16T07:41:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235102h60EkTlF2wSo5Yuz.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一款由 Kalon 设计工作室和 Nico Nico 联合设计的一款儿童帐篷，灵感来源于美国早期的迁徙运动。材质上采用纯天然木质结构和帆布，侧面设有一个可以打开的窗户。帆布有条纹，白色，黑色三种可以选择，内部空间宽敞，甚至可以达成一个小小剧院的样子。目前产品售价 320 美元，<a href=\"http://kalonstudios.com/shop/us/field-tent\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235058Tz6qHS5o7iDFpZvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235059vYjLX8huFE9z7G1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235059c4RlzgaGqO6XDpPe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052351009QKf0klVqgZMEyj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235100FVgwUy1QqmX9CiBb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523510112IDofOhY84reUKl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}